2026-05-14T06:36:16.1362452Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T06:36:16.1363033Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T06:36:16.1363893Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T06:36:16.1364713Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T06:36:16.1365538Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T06:36:16.1366249Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
